@DATABASE "Cauldron"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - C - Cauldron"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - C
                   ====================================

                                 Cauldron
                                 ========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(40060,0)"}          40060,0
@{"Infinite Hags " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(40055,0)"}          40055,0
@{"Infinite Magic" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(28602,0) ZXAMPoke(34756,0)"}          28602,0:34756,0

                         A couple of points:-

                         (1). The HAGS counter goes down, but don't worry.
                         (2). You can still DIE if you fall off the ledges
                              inside any of the buildings - can't be helped.

                                                                Rastan.
@endnode
